      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SOFT BEAUTY (5) was in the placings last time but shapes well for this on her solid win the start prior, getting around this track over 515m in 29.52. Smart win two back and looks a key chance here. TIGER ROCKS (1) is a capable type and proved too classy last time to win by 1.2 lengths at this track in a handy 30.07 beating Leviathan. Can measure up again. PAW GRADY (2) comes off an average effort last start when seventh at this track over 595m behind Urana Parallax (35.21) in a Grade 5. Goes very well from this draw with four wins and three minor placings from nine starts. Should be thereabouts. IN BLOOM (7) picked up a cheque last time and is in the mix again.",
